                <mxCell id="51YhVwraCw5KAQs0cLn3-45" value="&lt;div style=&quot;font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;border-color: var(--border-color);&quot;&gt;Control Panel (Master Node):&lt;/b&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;A special kind node running process to manage the reset of nodes (cluster) there is usually a replicate.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;Developer only interacts with Master node, and control the worker node from Master node&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;recommended to use multiple nodes as master for high availability and fault tolerance.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Kube API Server&lt;/b&gt;:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;expose k8s API to let user&amp;nbsp;query and manipulate the state of API objects&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;Authentication, Authorization, Admission&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;In High Availablility(HA) context, multiple API server runs in parallel in mumtiple control panel&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;Manifest:&amp;nbsp;etc/kubernetes/manifests/kube-apiserver.yaml&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: justify; font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: justify; font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Controller Manager&lt;/b&gt;:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: justify; font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: initial;&quot;&gt;includes a collection of &lt;b&gt;controllers &lt;/b&gt;that manages build-in k8s resource. Each controller is not aware of other controllers.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: justify; font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;In High Availablility(HA) context, only 1 Controller Manager run as the active one, while the rest are in standby mode&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: justify; font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: initial;&quot;&gt;controller that is responsible for signing certificate,&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: justify; font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: initial;&quot;&gt;the root CA certificate and key is set in /etc/kubernetes/manifests/kube-controller-manager.yaml&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: justify; font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;border-color: var(--border-color); text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: justify; font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Scheduler&lt;/b&gt;: Decides which pod runs on which node, deployed as pod in namespace kube-system&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: justify; font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;In High Availablility(HA) context, only 1 Scheduler run as the active one, while the rest are in standby mode&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: justify; font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;Manifest:&amp;nbsp;etc/kubernetes/manifests/kube-scheduler.yaml&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: justify; font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: justify; font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;border-color: var(--border-color); text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;border-color: var(--border-color);&quot;&gt;&lt;br class=&quot;Apple-interchange-newline&quot;&gt;Root CA&lt;/b&gt;:&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;border-color: var(--border-color); text-align: left;&quot;&gt;the Root CA Certificate and key in located in control panel&#39;s file system at&amp;nbsp;/etc/kubernetes/pki/&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;" parent="1" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="1795" y="-562" width="977" height="560" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="51YhVwraCw5KAQs0cLn3-61" value="&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Worker Node:&lt;/b&gt;&amp;nbsp;is either a virtual / physical server&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;pre style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Helvetica&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;kubelet:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;acts as node manager, managing/maintaining containers on that node, create/delete pod&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;keeps pulling from API server in master node to watch changes and check there is any job assigned to it&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;/var/lib/kubelet/config.yaml configures the kubelet&#39;s operation and behavior on the node.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;/etc/kubernetes/kubelet.conf configures the kubelet&#39;s credentials and how it communicates with the Kubernetes API server.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;kube-proxy:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;deployed as &lt;b&gt;pod&lt;/b&gt; by &lt;b&gt;daemonSet&lt;/b&gt;, maintains network rules, allow network communication to pod form inside/outside the cluster. it maintains iptables (routing table),&amp;nbsp; looks for new service, communicates with&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: initial;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;API server in master node to watch changes&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: initial;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Pod&lt;/strong&gt;:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;single instance of an application&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;Pods are ephemeral. They come and go at any time&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;the smallest deployable unit, scaling creates new pod, but application is hosted in container&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;pod can have &lt;strong&gt;multiple container&lt;/strong&gt; with shared storage and network within it&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;pods are created and managed by control plane&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;pod name should be unique within the same namespace&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;typically all containers would have the same access level, network segmentation, and identity&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;background-color: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;background-color: initial;&quot;&gt;Container runtime Interface&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: initial;&quot;&gt;:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;background-color: initial;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;API used to enable integration between the kubele and various container runtimes, e.g., Docker.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 15px; background-color: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 15px; background-color: initial;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 15px; background-color: initial;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot; title=&quot;Page 32&quot; class=&quot;page&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 15px; background-color: initial;&quot;&gt;All&amp;nbsp;&lt;b&gt;containers&lt;/b&gt; in a &lt;/span&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: initial;&quot;&gt;Pod share the same IP address, hostname and port range, and are deployed and scaled together, can also share filesystem.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;&quot;&gt;However, applications in different Pods are isolated from each other; they have different IP addresses, hostnames, and more&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;font-size: 15px;&quot; class=&quot;layoutArea&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;column&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;" parent="1" vertex="1">
